/**
 * Padding map referenced in:
 *  - Popover
 *  - PageContentHeader
 *  - PageContentHeaderSection
*/
$euiPanelPaddingModifiers: (
  'paddingSmall': $euiSizeS,
  'paddingMedium': $euiSize,
  'paddingLarge': $euiSizeL
) !default;

$euiPanelBorderColor: tintOrShade($euiShadowColor, 40%, 0%) !default; // match shadow
$euiDatePickerCalendarWidth: 284px;

$euiSuperDatePickerWidth: $euiSize * 30;
$euiSuperDatePickerButtonWidth: $euiButtonMinWidth + ($euiSizeXS * 1.5);
$euiTextConstrainedMaxWidth: 36em;
$euiSelectableListItemBorder: 1px solid darken($euiColorLightestShade, 2%);
